data.title: Best takeout in middle Georgia!
data.text: This is the place to go for quick take out of  a endless selection of fresh fish. Get it cooked or raw! They will cook it to your desire! Friendly service and cater.

data.title: local fish market
data.text: First time there. This local sea food store, There are several Fish Houses 1,2,3,4 get picture. They sell Fish, shrimp and few other thing. They will cook your food at extra cost. They also have a lunch and dinner menu like any other place. They have couple tables to eat there, We took our order home. Food was ok and you get decent amount. I had catfish platter and girl friend had fried shrimps platter yes that whats on the sign fried shrimps lol.
